project_descr: The programme seeks to support the implementation of the constitution in particular the Bill of Rights, transparence and accontability.  It is also aims to supports the national response to gender based violence.

outputs.output_descr: Fundamental principles and practices for good governance will be built for key national institutions for effective management of public resources, access to justice and information.
